extendedInfo.description: This slot machine is 100% free. We don't charge you for credits or levels like other machines.Diamond Slots Progressive Slot Machine is a Vegas inspired slot machine for your mobile device or tablet. A lot of research went into this app to provide the gamer with the most realistic slot machine experience.Diamond Slots features a progressive payout system if you're lucky enough to hit it! It also features icons that will double your payout. Some of the other reels consist of triple 7's, double 7s single 7s, jackpot bar, and jackpot 5 bar. Don't like the background noise? You can easily disable it in the menu by pressing the menu key and clicking on "Background Sounds". Other features include swipe down at any time to see the payout list. Play max credits by pressing the search button on your phone. Submit your score to the high score list. You can also retrieve your score if your phone ever loses it for any reason.Tags: double diamond slots diamond slot machine slotsfree bonusslots slotmachine triple quality quarter leaderboard score coins credits free high roller cashier purchases achievements bonuses jackpot slotsfree
